## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="f7a72-109"><xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ReceiveContext.Abandon%2A> potrebbe bloccarsi quando è presente una transazione di ambiente e <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ReceiveContext.Complete%2A> viene chiamato e successivamente viene eseguito il rollback di transazione.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7a72-109"><xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ReceiveContext.Abandon%2A> may hang when there is an ambient transaction and <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ReceiveContext.Complete%2A> is called and afterwards the transaction is rolled back.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f7a72-110">Se <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ReceiveContext.Abandon%2A> viene chiamato prima del completamento rollback di transazione, sarà presente una race condition, causando la chiamata a <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ReceiveContext.Abandon%2A> il blocco.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7a72-110">If <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ReceiveContext.Abandon%2A> is called prior to the transaction rollback completing, a race condition will exist, causing the call to <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ReceiveContext.Abandon%2A> to hang.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f7a72-111">Ciò può essere illustrato nel seguente esempio di pseudocodice</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7a72-111">This can be illustrated by the following pseudo-code example</span></span>  
  
```  
using (TransactionScope ts = new TransactionScope())   
{  
   try  
   {  
       rc.Complete();  
      ...  
   }  
   Catch (Exception)   
   {  
      rc.Abandon()  
   }  
}  
  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="f7a72-112">Non si tratta il modello consigliato per l'utilizzo di T:System.ServiceModel.Channels.RecieveContext.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7a72-112">This is not the recommended pattern for working with T:System.ServiceModel.Channels.RecieveContext.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f7a72-113">In alternativa, è consigliabile inserire il blocco try/catch di fuori dell'ambito della transazione.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7a72-113">Instead the try/catch block should be placed outside of the transaction scope.</span></span>

